<acqinfo encodinganalog="541" id="a19">
<head>Acquisition Information</head>
<p>In 1968, the records were brought to the Special Collections Department. They were then transferred to Historical Manuscripts and Archives in August 1979 and were arranged and described in the spring of 1980. In 1995, Special Collections and Historical Manuscripts and Archives merged to form Archives &#x0026; Special Collections and were relocated to the Thomas J. Dodd Research Center. </p>

